OL,3,CRapist given 7-year jail sentence
OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,FA rapist who repeatedly altered his
OL,8,Faccount of events in an attempt to
OL,9,Favoid conviction has been sentenced to
OL,10,Fseven and a half years in prison.
OL,12,FJordan Hewitt, aged 33 and from
OL,13,FThorverton, received his sentence at
OL,14,FExeter Crown Court on the 25th July,
OL,15,Ffollowing his conviction for rape.
