OL,3,CRapist given 7-year jail sentence
OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,FShe immediately pushed Hewitt away and
OL,8,Ftelephoned her mother for transport
OL,9,Fhome, immediately telling her what had
OL,10,Foccurred.
OL,12,FLater that day, the victim sent Hewitt
OL,13,Fa Facebook message asking: "Why did
OL,14,Fyou do that to me?".
OL,16,FHewitt completely dismissed her
OL,17,Fquestion, instead asking if she had
OL,18,Farrived home safely and suggesting she
OL,19,Fcould ring him if she wished. She
OL,20,Fsubsequently blocked him on Facebook.
