OL,3,CRapist given 7-year jail sentence
OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,FThree weeks later, Hewitt encountered
OL,8,Fone of the victim's friends, who
OL,9,Fsecretly recorded him giving his
OL,10,Finitial version of events.
OL,12,FIn this recording, Hewitt admitted to
OL,13,Fpenetrating the victim before stopping
OL,14,Fwhen she pushed him away.
OL,16,FDuring this account, Hewitt appeared
OL,17,Fto attempt to justify his actions
OL,18,Fsaying, "She clearly met me for a bit
OL,19,Fof fun".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
