OL,3,CRapist given 7-year jail sentence
OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,FHe was also recorded threatening that
OL,8,Fthe victim would be forced to leave
OL,9,Ftown and would be assaulted if the
OL,10,Fmatter proceeded to court.
OL,12,FWhen interviewed, Hewitt claimed the
OL,13,Fvictim had initiated sexual contact.
OL,14,FHe initially denied making any threats
OL,15,Fof violence against the victim.
OL,17,FWhen confronted with part of the
OL,18,Fsecret recording containing the
OL,19,Fthreat, he changed his story,
OL,20,Fadmitting to making the threat but
OL,21,Fclaiming he didn't mean it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
