OL,3,CRapist given 7-year jail sentence
OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,FThe complete secret recording was then
OL,8,Fplayed to Hewitt, containing his
OL,9,Faccount of the incident. This caused
OL,10,Fhim to panic and alter his story once
OL,11,Fagain, now claiming the victim hadn't
OL,12,Ftold him to stop, but there had been
OL,13,F"a bit of a strange moment where she
OL,14,Fappeared to back away".
OL,16,FBy the time the case reached court,
OL,17,FHewitt had changed his account again,
OL,18,Fstating in his defence that he had
OL,19,Fbeen too intoxicated to engage in
OL,20,Fsexual activity.
