OL,7,FDuring cross examination, he altered
OL,8,Fhis account once again, stating the
OL,9,Fpair did not have sex because the
OL,10,Fvictim was facing away from him.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Andrew Stacey from
OL,13,FExeter CID, the officer on the case,
OL,14,Fcommented: "We welcome the sentence
OL,15,Fimposed by the court, which wouldn't
OL,16,Fhave been achievable without the
OL,17,Fbravery and continued cooperation of
OL,18,Fthe victim throughout our
OL,19,Finvestigation.
