OL,4,Cafter admitting to crimes on secret
OL,5,Crecording
OL,7,F"I would also like to thank all
OL,8,Fwitnesses who came forward to give
OL,9,Fevidence, particularly one person
OL,10,Fwhose presence of mind in covertly
OL,11,Frecording one of Hewitt's accounts was
OL,12,Finstrumental in exposing his continued
OL,13,Fdeception.
OL,15,F"Hewitt is a manipulative individual
OL,16,Fwho demonstrated complete disregard
OL,17,Ffor the person he harmed. His
OL,18,Fpersistent dishonesty and repeated
OL,19,Falterations to his story ultimately
OL,20,Fsealed his fate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
